{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d4d31c5733","title":"对王明来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2fb2f0aded","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"d4d31c5733"}],"tags":[{"id":"1f0832775e","name":"王明","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"7085288ac4","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王明，即陈绍禹，当时任中共中央委员、中央人民政府法制委员会主任委员。他在1950年8月17日给毛泽东并中央书记处写信，要求中央明确指出他应在多长时间内写成声明书，对他在十年内战时期和抗日战争时期所写各种文章、小册子及其他文件进行检讨；并提出为了进行检讨，希望将1937年12月会议散会时收去的笔记本还给他，希望借用武汉时期的《新华日报》和延安的《新中华报》。"},{"id":"0bc24a0e94","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。任，指任弱时。尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"255cc06e29","type":"title","text":"对王明来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733"},{"id":"7085288ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、朱、任、尚昆阅","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733"},{"id":"0bc24a0e94","type":"paragraph","text":"王明的声明书应在十一月上句七届四中全会开会以前写好，并送交政治局。王明的笔记本及武汉时期的报纸，请尚昆清查是否尚有保存。以上两点，由尚昆口头通知王明","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733"},{"id":"85f1704507","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733"},{"id":"821d0fb4cc","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733"}],"page":{"id":"09e30e86f9","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4d31c5733","start":89,"end":89}}}},"__N_SSG":true}